      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one and is truly flawless inside and out. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how perfect it is. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
