    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in collector-grade condition. This A80 chassis remains in its original, unmodified configuration, powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six. The powertrain is paired with the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Technical inspection confirms perfect compression across all cylinders and a pristine undercarriage with zero oxidation. The double-wishbone suspension retains its factory damping characteristics, and the four-piston front calipers provide firm, consistent bite. This is a rare, time-capsule specimen featuring original VIN tags on all panels and a flawless interior, representing the pinnacle of 90s JDM performance engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
